  <h2 class="text-4xl font-medium mb-6 text-[#957B44]">What is Datastar?</h2>
  <p class="text-xl leading-10 mb-4">
    Datastar is a lightweight hypermedia framework that brings reactive functionality to server-rendered applications.
    It combines the best of both worlds:
  </p>
  <ul class="block list-disc ml-8 mb-4 list-image-[url(/images/arrow-right.svg)]">
    <li>The simplicity and reliability of server-side rendering</li>
    <li>
      The dynamic, reactive user experience in the style of a Single Page Application (SPA) but with very little to no
      JavaScript
    </li>
  </ul>
</section>

